{"tid":141561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果私營籃球聯賽僱主欠工資一年唔出糧點算好","createTime":"2017-03-03T04:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T13:27:28.000Z","uid":46813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa0ad36d84b5fb00d4e76b6c491c7eedebab05f","tid":141561,"uid":46813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"事緣上年因為工餘有時間希望幫下手做籃球聯賽做計分員。咁做完八個鐘，佢原本話出現金，但最後都唔肯出，又要我俾全職個份合約，又要我俾公司證明我可以做兼職嘅文件先。直到而家都足足一年，佢都未肯出返糧。<br />\n<br />\n咁我最緊見佢聯賽又收隊伍，咪問下佢出糧未。亦都同佢講話唔出俾我都唔緊要，你咪捐去無國界囉。點知佢又係到拖拖拉拉，各位巴打有無建議點做好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ryjw2dmz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fryjw2dmz&h=fe95de16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pxz35blg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpxz35blg&h=c4c1f9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3olf1x2i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3olf1x2i&h=bdfbd9bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9941ea8c7496093f33fe9fbf39adf307d20ef128","tid":141561,"uid":46813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd8e6606f8784259a24f25a0b0586fe5bba7ad95","tid":141561,"uid":46813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438d691e71d1eb40fdaf060fa4abf6c675b16913","tid":141561,"uid":46813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74447ba21a816b2696d74fc85db38b24134af403","tid":141561,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"